Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE are pleased to present to the market for sale via Expressions of Interest, 1362 Lytton Road, Hemmant.

Situated in Hemmant, this freehold site offers unrivalled exposure being located on a main road (Lytton Road). The subject property offers easy access to the Gateway Arterial North and South and is also in close proximity to the Port of Brisbane.

This offering appeals to any prospective owner occupier and/or investor with endless opportunity. With a significant increase in buyer demand and limited land supply, especially freehold lots of this size, this opportunity is one NOT to miss! 

Some of the property features include:

• 1,440sqm* of GI land situated on a highly exposed site 
• Entire site is covered with commercial grade concrete 
• Approx. 30m frontage to main road (Lytton Road) & 40 frontage to Aquarium Ave 
• 300sqm* functional metal clad warehouse for storage 
• Fully fenced and secured site
*Approx.

For further information or to arrange your inspection, please contact Exclusive Agents Ben Lyons of CBRE today.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: BITE SIZED FREEHOLD LAND ON OFFER!

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is excited to present to the market for sale via Expressions of Interest, 95 Aquarium Ave, Hemmant. With limited freehold parcels of land available within an increasingly tight market, this property is a must see for any potential occupier or investor/developer.

Hemmant which is situated approx. 14klm from the Brisbane CBD and on the doorstep of the Port of Brisbane, remains one of the most highly sought after industrial hubs within the Southern Tradecoast. This site is located just off main Lytton Road which provides direct access onto both the Gateway & Port of Brisbane Motorways.

Some features of the property are:

•	1ha freehold parcel zoned General Industry
•	Fully fenced and secured site
•	Duel crossovers for easy truck access
•	Approx. 100mts of water frontage with slipway
•	Wet leases in place with the site 
•	Potential opportunity for a short term leaseback
•	Development upside or opportunity to secure tenant income 

This site is being offered via Expressions of Interest closing Wednesday 23rd October 2019 at 4PMAEST (if not sold prior).

For further information regarding this extremely rare opportunity, please contact Exclusive Agent Ben Lyons of CBRE.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: RARE 1HA FREEHOLD LAND IN THE PORT!

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
The site comprises multiple allotments providing an overall irregular shaped parcel, which is relatively level over its total area. There are three allotments on Kianawah Road, with the balance land accessed via Burnby Road.

Features include:

+ Land area of 22.56ha*
+ Multiple allotments
+ Large land holding in fast growing residential area
+ Multiple redevelopment opportunities available (STCA)
+ Close to schools, public transport and local infrastructure

The property is available for sale via Expressions of Interest campaign closing Wednesday 2nd October 2019 at 4:00pm AEST. 

For additional information please contact the exclusive agent.


*Approximate

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: DEVELOPMENT OPPORTUNITY IN THE HEART OF HEMMANT

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Warehouse / Office / Storage / Yard.

Where else can you find it all under the one roof? This unit contains 25-50sqm office / 304sqm warehouse with yard areas & ample car parking. Perfect for those sick of tight industrial complexes. The freestanding building has it all.
